OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fshowers fade leaving clear spells for
OL,7,Fmany. Rain may persist in the far
OL,8,Fnorth of northern England. Chilly with
OL,9,Fa local frost possible in the
OL,10,Fnorthwest, as well as a rural grass
OL,11,Ffrost and isolated fog patches further
OL,12,Fsouth.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FA band of rain moves south
OL,15,Facross Scotland, Northern Ireland and
OL,16,Fnorthern England. Scattered heavy
OL,17,Fshowers in Wales and the Midlands.
OL,18,FFeeling warm in the south, but colder
OL,19,Ffurther north.
